WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.367 --> 00:00:12.413
Pinch to enter the edit mode

00:00:12.413 --> 00:00:19.628
Slide to the the left or right

00:00:19.628 --> 00:00:24.843
Tap the "Add" icon to add a page

00:00:24.843 --> 00:00:30.458
Tap the "Delete" icon at top right corner to delete the page

00:00:30.458 --> 00:00:35.118
Tap the "Home" icon at top left corner

00:00:35.118 --> 00:00:41.120
It's make the page as home page

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:43.635
Tap the "Apps" icon to open apps drawer

00:00:43.635 --> 00:00:47.524
Slide to right and select the sorting order

00:00:47.524 --> 00:01:00.081
You can only change the order of apps in "Own order" sorting

00:01:00.081 --> 00:01:05.669
Tap and hold the app you want, drop it to the position you want

00:01:05.669 --> 00:01:09.495
To create a folder, drag and drop the app to another

00:01:09.495 --> 00:01:18.776
To change the folder's name,
open the folder and tap the name to edit

00:01:18.776 --> 00:01:27.976
To remove a folder, drag the apps out of the folder

00:01:27.976 --> 00:01:37.013
Tap and drag the apps to top to make a shortcut in homescreen

00:01:37.013 --> 00:01:42.570
Tap and drag the shortcut to change the position

00:01:42.570 --> 00:01:48.521
To create a folder, drag and drop the shortcut to another

00:01:48.520 --> 00:01:55.984
To remove a folder or shortcut,
drag and drop the folder or shortcut to the bottom

00:01:55.984 --> 00:01:59.180
Pinch to enter the edit mode

00:01:59.180 --> 00:02:01.422
Tap "Widgets"

00:02:01.422 --> 00:02:12.737
Tap and drag the widget to the page you want

00:02:12.737 --> 00:02:22.365
Tap and drag the widget to change the position

00:02:22.365 --> 00:02:34.693
Tap and hold the widget to enter edit mode,
tap the edge and drag to change the size

00:02:34.693 --> 00:02:40.252
To remove the widget,
Drag and drop it to the bottom

